Name: Wheels of Duty
About the game: Fight Against other players online across multiple locations with multiple game modes. Set in a world where a deadly virus has caused everyone to lose their ability to use there legs, players must roll around in there wheel chairs and fulfill there duty as a soldier and claim victory on the battle ground. Wheels of Duty Contains multiple game modes Team Death Match - utilize different guns and abilities to your advantage and fight in a team to defeat you enemy. Free for All - every one is your enemy, put them in there graves first. Gun Game - like free for all but you must progress through all the guns in the game by killing your enemies to win. Zombies - Band together in a group of up to 4 player to survive against zombies in rounds of increasing difficulty Join the discord to voice ur opinions and ideas on how to improve the game
